name.text: 6.0.3 (Centre and radius of circle from graph)

questiontext.text:
Find the coordinates of the centre and the radius of the following circle

  • Radius = [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]][[feedback:prt1]]
  • Centre = ([[input:ans21]] [[validation:ans21]],[[input:ans22]] [[validation:ans22]])[[feedback:prt2]]

generalfeedback.text: We can see here from looking at the axes, that the radius is {@ta1@}. Similarly the centre is the point ({@ta21@},{@ta22@})
